.TH AGENT-HOOK-NOTIFICATION 1 "2026-06-30" "agentguard" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
agent-hook-notification \- play terminal notifications for agent events
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agent-hook-notification
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B agent-hook-notification
reads an agent notification hook payload from standard input and plays the
configured terminal notification sound. It does not add workflow warnings or
blocks.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
The notification was emitted or skipped by best-effort terminal handling.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR agent-hook-stop (1)
